			"value": "<p><em>You blast nearby creatures with magical and extremely loud noise.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 30 ft. Cone - Magical - 1 Round</p><p>You expend a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die to use this ability.</p><p><strong>Constitution Save</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Failure:</strong> Thunder damage equal to three rolls of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die and target is deafened.</li><li><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</li></ul>",
